<standards>
- Always inherit from base models in `apps/common/models/base.py`.
- Keep views thin; delegate logic to services/selectors.
- Services own writes/business rules; selectors own reads.
- Apply DRY/SOLID/KISS without premature abstraction.
- Line length: 100.
</standards>
